d","text":"On nights with many shooting stars, CLEFFA can be seen dancing in a ring. They dance until daybreak, when they quench their thirst with the morning dew."},{"version":"firered","text":"When numerous meteors illuminate the night sky, sightings of CLEFFA strangely increase."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Because of its unusual, starlike silhouette, people believe that it came here on a meteor."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Its silhouette is like a star. It is believed to arrive riding on shooting stars."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Many appear when the night skies are filled with shooting stars. They disappear with sunrise."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It is often seen when shooting stars fill the night skies. It\u2019s said to arrive riding on a shooting star."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Because of its unusual, starlike silhouette, people believe that it came here on a meteor."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"When numerous meteors illuminate the night sky, sightings of CLEFFA strangely increase."},{"version":"black","text":"It is often seen when shooting stars fill the night skies. It\u2019s said to arrive riding on a shooting star."},{"version":"white","text":"It is often seen when shooting stars fill the night skies. It\u2019s said to arrive riding on a shooting star."},{"version":"black-2","text":"According to local rumors, Cleffa are often seen in places where shooting stars have fallen."},{"version":"white-2","text":"According to local rumors, Cleffa are often seen in places where shooting stars have fallen."},{"version":"x","text":"Because of its unusual, starlike silhouette, people believe that it came here on a meteor."},{"version":"y","text":"Many appear when the night skies are filled with shooting stars. They disappear with sunrise."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"On nights with many shooting stars, they gather in packs and dance in circles. If you should see them, something good will happen!"},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"On nights with many shooting stars, Cleffa can be seen dancing in a ring. They dance through the night and stop only at the break of day, when these Pok\u00e9mon quench their thirst with the morning dew."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"On nights with many shooting stars, Cleffa can be seen dancing in a ring. They dance through the night and stop only at the break of day, when these Pok\u00e9mon quench their thirst with the morning dew."},{"version":"sun","text":"On late nights illuminated by shooting stars, it gazes intently skyward, as if thinking of its home."},{"version":"moon","text":"Because of its silhouette, it\u2019s believed to be a star reborn. For some reason, it loves Minior."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Said to have ridden here on a shooting star, Cleffa seem to appear in places where meteorites have struck in the past."},{"version":"sword","text":"According to local rumors, Cleffa are often seen in places where shooting stars have fallen."},{"version":"shield","text":"Because of its unusual, starlike silhouette, people believe that it came here on a meteor."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"In silhouette, they resemble twinkling starlight. When shooting stars rain from the night sky, Cleffa gather in numbers and dance as though they are indeed incarnations of the stars."}],"evo":{"name":"cleffa","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"clefairy","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":160,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"clefable","level":2,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"moon-stone","h